<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="mscc0359a15daoJiao"><head>宋<placeName key="PL000000011077">龍華寺</placeName><persName key="A014019">釋道矯</persName></head><p><anchor n="X.77.1523.0359a15"/><lb ed="X" n="0359a15"/>道矯<placeName key="PL000000042697">高陸</placeName>人也。性清約。蔬食禪誦。住<placeName key="PL000000011077">龍花寺</placeName>。專當寺<lb ed="X" n="0359a16"/>任。恪居客眾。<date from-iso="0439-02-01" to-iso="0440-02-19" key="j18814331881816">元嘉十六年</date>。磬率衣資。開誘聞業。與<placeName key="PL000000008975">建<lb ed="X" n="0359a17"/>康</placeName>民<persName key="A018961">朱舛孫</persName>。共起佛殿三間。并諸花幡。造夾苧彌勒<lb ed="X" n="0359a18"/>佛倚像一軀。高一丈六尺。神儀端儼。開發信悟。春秋<lb ed="X" n="0359a19"/>九十三。<date from-iso="0449-02-10" to-iso="0450-01-29" key="j18850951885448">二十六年</date>卒(云云)。</p>
